Prefix	Meaning
gv_	Global variable
lv_	Local variable
gs_	Global structure (one row)
ls_	Local structure
gt_	Global internal table
lt_	Local internal table


Why ABAP especially cares about this

In real projects:
Programs are thousands of lines
Many people touch the same code
You debug code written 10 years ago
Good naming = faster understanding = fewer mistakes

Common Prefix

p_	Single input parameter
s_	Select-options (range input)
pa_	Parameter (some teams use this)
